You said you're not forcing me.

27
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,720
But if I don't make up with my dad,

28
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,120
you will break up with me.

29
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,690
I don't know what this has to do with it.

30
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,780
The love I want

31
00:02:49,050 --> 00:02:50,700
is like my parents' love.

32
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,660
Although they quarrel

33
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:54,020
for trivial things

34
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:55,540
every day,

35
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:58,190
their love won't fade away.

36
00:02:58,190 --> 00:03:00,260
Because they have the same values.

37
00:03:01,530 --> 00:03:03,130
But we are really different.

38
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,520
I think money is very important.

39
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,970
So I'm frugal.

40
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,840
But because of your dad,

41
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,780
you hate money.

42
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:16,120
If you can't resolve your inner conflict,

43
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:18,530
there will always be friction between us.

44
00:03:19,810 --> 00:03:22,740
Do you think this kind of relationship can last long?

45
00:03:55,329 --> 00:03:56,540
Here's your change.

46
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,360
Thank you.

47
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,420
Please come again.

48
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,330
Welcome.

49
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,250
Why are you here?

50
00:04:12,130 --> 00:04:13,520
It's all Manager's fault.

51
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,320
On the opening day,

52
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,890
he insisted on scheduling a shift for me.

53
00:04:15,890 --> 00:04:17,459
So I couldn't come to celebrate with you.

54
00:04:17,459 --> 00:04:19,459
That's why I came as soon as I'm free.

55
00:04:19,459 --> 00:04:20,529
They made me lose

56
00:04:20,529 --> 00:04:21,790
two employees in one go.

57
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:22,990
I'm short-handed.

58
00:04:24,610 --> 00:04:26,000
Manager, Qianqian.

59
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,140
-Jiali.
-Jiali.

60
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:28,560
Congratulations. You really have opened a store.

61
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,230
Thank you.

62
00:04:29,230 --> 00:04:30,950
I smelt the bread's fragrance from afar.

63
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:33,420
They must be made by Jiali,

64
00:04:33,450 --> 00:04:35,140
Yuanchong's girlfriend.

65
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,390
What do you want to eat today?

66
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,010
My treat.

67
00:04:43,659 --> 00:04:44,760
Really?

68
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,500
Let me do it.

69
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,490
No need for that.

70
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:57,290
They all smell so good.

71
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:01,360
Don't you think they're weird?

72
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,940
They don't have any of the intimacy

73
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:04,470
you'd expect from a couple.

74
00:05:04,670 --> 00:05:05,640
It's not good

75
00:05:05,670 --> 00:05:07,380
to act intimately during work.

76
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,060
Now they're behaving

77
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:10,010
more distantly than us.

78
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,730
So?

79
00:05:13,470 --> 00:05:14,560
Based on my experience,

80
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,490
they are

81
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:16,490
on the outs.

82
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,110
When my wife and I

83
00:05:18,110 --> 00:05:19,910
-have a disagreement,
-Really?

84
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:22,430
we'd give each other the silent treatment.

85
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:24,730
We'd pretend not to see each other.

86
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:26,840
I can see.

87
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:29,790
You heard it?

88
00:05:29,790 --> 00:05:30,650
Invisible man.

89
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,090
It's my lunch break now.

90
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:35,840
I can't have lunch with you.

91
00:05:37,290 --> 00:05:38,020
It's okay.

92
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:38,890
Our plan is

93
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:39,680
to eat with you

94
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,030
after you get off work.

95
00:05:43,450 --> 00:05:44,650
It's not convenient.

96
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:46,909
Why?

97
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:50,090
I need to clean this place after work.

98
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:50,860
It'll be very tiring.

99
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:52,460
I just want to go home to rest.

100
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:54,230
I'll be back in about an hour.

101
00:05:54,890 --> 00:05:55,830
Then you can go out

102
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,230
to have lunch with Jiali.

103
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,440
Is this for me?

104
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:14,920
It's not for you.

105
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,880
We're here to exchange money with you.

106
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:20,580
Aunt,

107
00:06:21,350 --> 00:06:23,280
I know you need 500,000 NT dollars.

108
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,520
So, I would like to ask you

109
00:06:25,990 --> 00:06:28,160
to give the 300,000 NT dollars you borrowed from Jiali

110
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,840
back to her

111
00:06:29,770 --> 00:06:30,850
and tell her

112
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,990
you don't need the money anymore.

113
00:06:32,990 --> 00:06:34,350
You mean...

114
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,780
you'll lend me money?

115
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:38,909
Yes.

116
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,060
Because Jiali

117
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,140
needs her money to run the store.

118
00:06:43,730 --> 00:06:44,590
I don't want her

119
00:06:44,909 --> 00:06:47,570
to be easily held back from achieving her dream.

120
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:52,460
You also know Jiali needs money to run her store,

121
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:54,250
but you still borrowed money from her.

122
00:06:54,250 --> 00:06:55,300
How dare you!

123
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:55,890
Mom,

124
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,490
-I...
-Stop talking.

125
00:06:58,659 --> 00:07:01,190
Return the money to Jiali as soon as possible.

126
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:03,440
Tell your husband to find a job as soon as possible

127
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:06,370
so that you can pay back the money borrowed from Yuan.

128
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:09,020
It's okay even if you

129
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:10,420
don't pay back the money.

130
00:07:10,930 --> 00:07:12,300
W-What?

131
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:14,160
It's not okay.

132
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:15,090
But...

133
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:17,250
I hope

134
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,570
you can promise me one thing.

135
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:22,850
What is it?

136
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,980
I hope you

137
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:28,220
can contact Jiali frequently.

138
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,760
It's okay even if it's just a simple greeting.

139
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,900
How are you?

140
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,360
How have you been?

141
00:07:35,170 --> 00:07:36,430
How is your work going?

142
00:07:36,450 --> 00:07:39,050
It's also okay if you just ask her if she's full.

143
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,370
I want Jiali

144
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:43,780
to feel more cared-for.

145
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,270
Look.

146
00:07:48,890 --> 00:07:51,350
Even Yuan knows he should treat Jiali well.

147
00:07:51,909 --> 00:07:53,250
As her mother,

148
00:07:53,350 --> 00:07:55,150
you haven't even given her a greeting.

149
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,560
She's your daughter too!

150
00:07:58,020 --> 00:07:59,980
Grandma, don't be angry.

151
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:08,170
Of course I can do that.

152
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:10,070
In the past,

153
00:08:10,550 --> 00:08:13,230
my youngest daughter was still little.

154
00:08:13,450 --> 00:08:14,930
I really couldn't spare time,

155
00:08:14,930 --> 00:08:16,530
so I ignored Jiali.

156
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,030
But I can do it now.

157
00:08:20,090 --> 00:08:21,730
Jiali is my daughter.

158
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:23,530
Of course I would care about her.

159
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:25,450
Thank you.

160
00:08:31,930 --> 00:08:33,010
I thought

161
00:08:33,669 --> 00:08:36,130
you asked me to ask Jiali's mother to come out

162
00:08:36,130 --> 00:08:38,220
because you wanted her to pay back the money.

163
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:39,490
Instead, you gave her money

164
00:08:39,490 --> 00:08:41,419
and asked her to return it to Jiali.

165
00:08:41,570 --> 00:08:43,419
Why are you so silly?

166
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:44,700
Grandma,

167
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:46,080
I'm not silly.

168
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,210
I just chose

169
00:08:48,490 --> 00:08:49,290
the current best solution

170
00:08:49,290 --> 00:08:50,890
for Jiali.

171
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:52,670
I think

172
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:54,170
I'm very smart.

173
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:59,170
Don't be mad at Jiali.

174
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,640
Since you left that day,

175
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,260
she's been very upset after she came back

176
00:09:03,260 --> 00:09:04,690
from work every day.

177
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:07,620
She has barely eaten.

178
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,300
Really?

179
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,060
Why would I lie to you?

180
00:09:14,090 --> 00:09:15,760
Actually, I know

181
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:18,930
Jiali cares about you very much.

182
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,260
I know.

183
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:24,500
So I'm not mad at her.

184
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:27,720
She said she lacks love.

185
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:29,270
As her boyfriend,

186
00:09:29,410 --> 00:09:31,070
I should give her lots of love.

187
00:09:31,580 --> 00:09:32,710
Yes.

188
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,730
Great.

189
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,510
When you left that day,

190
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,430
I saw your facial expression.

191
00:09:38,460 --> 00:09:39,940
You looked very hurt.

192
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,550
I was so worried.

193
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:42,850
I was worried you suffered a blow

194
00:09:42,850 --> 00:09:44,980
and wouldn't dare to love her anymore.

195
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,050
Don't worry, Grandma.

196
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:49,440
Even if I feel hurt,

197
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,270
I'll become stronger

198
00:09:51,340 --> 00:09:52,670
and love Jiali forever.

199
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:53,470
Yes.

200
00:09:53,690 --> 00:09:55,380
Great!

201
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:57,150
I love you too.

202
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,370
Thank you, Grandma.

203
00:09:58,930 --> 00:09:59,500
Let's go.

204
00:10:11,070 --> 00:10:11,870
What's wrong?

205
00:10:13,070 --> 00:10:14,870
Somehow, my shoes

206
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:17,000
are chafing my feet today.

207
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:19,020
Really?

208
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:26,360
What are you doing?

209
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,420
What are you doing?

210
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:30,840
No, put me down.

211
00:10:31,490 --> 00:10:32,780
L-Look.

212
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,620
Someone...

213
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:35,120
is watching us.

214
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:37,040
So what?

215
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,630
I'd rather let them watch us

216
00:10:40,330 --> 00:10:41,150
than let your feet

217
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:43,030
feel any discomfort.

218
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,030
Let's go.

219
00:10:54,730 --> 00:10:56,390
I'm going to order something.

220
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:03,540
Excuse me?

221
00:11:03,990 --> 00:11:04,700
Min.

222
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,470
Oscar?

223
00:11:07,730 --> 00:11:08,620
Long time no see.

224
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:10,370
Long time no see.

225
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,160
Just now, why...

226
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:15,670
My shoes are chafing my feet.

227
00:11:16,190 --> 00:11:17,320
Still exaggerated.

228
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,060
Yes.

229
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:27,930
No.

230
00:11:29,390 --> 00:11:29,970
Elly.

231
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,460
Your friend?

232
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:34,130
He was my classmate in Singapore.

233
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,350
Hello.

234
00:11:35,710 --> 00:11:36,510
I'm Michael.

235
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:37,430
I'm Oscar.

236
00:11:38,010 --> 00:11:38,650
Hello.

237
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:42,600
I'm her boyfriend.

238
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:46,970
Okay.

239
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:48,970
Why don't we...

240
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,350
friend each other?

241
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:53,610
-Okay.
-It'll be easier to contact each other in the future.

242
00:11:53,610 --> 00:11:54,620
Just contact me.

243
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,840
If you want to get in touch with Elly,

244
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,780
just contact me.

245
00:12:03,410 --> 00:12:04,080
Okay.

246
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:19,560
Baby, do your feet feel uncomfortable?

247
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:20,090
No.

248
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:21,620
Let me carry you.

249
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:22,550
No need for that.

250
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:25,090
Right,

251
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:27,080
send me the contact information

252
00:12:27,110 --> 00:12:28,440
of my former classmate.

253
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:31,380
It'll be weird if we contact each other through you.

254
00:12:31,570 --> 00:12:32,740
I'm your boyfriend.

255
00:12:32,770 --> 00:12:33,760
I think it's fine.

256
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:34,760
It won't be weird.

257
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,900
But he's my former classmate.

258
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,690
My former classmate...

259
00:12:43,690 --> 00:12:44,360
is your former classmate.

260
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,100
Your former classmate is my former classmate.

261
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:47,900
We are on intimate terms, right?

262
00:12:48,850 --> 00:12:50,170
But...

263
00:12:51,870 --> 00:12:53,290
It's great to meet you here.

264
00:12:53,290 --> 00:12:56,250
The shop offers a 50% discount on the second cup of coffee.

265
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,110
You... don't want coffee, right?

266
00:12:58,140 --> 00:12:59,740
Elly, do you want a cup?

267
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:02,390
If it's your treat,

268
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:04,190
I don't mind having another cup.

269
00:13:04,730 --> 00:13:05,600
I want one too.

270
00:13:07,580 --> 00:13:09,840
You don't drink excitant drinks, right?

271
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:14,370
It's okay to drink a cup occasionally, right?

272
00:13:15,010 --> 00:13:16,540
But if both of you want a cup,

273
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,040
you can already get a 50% discount on the second cup.

274
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:18,500
Well...

275
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:19,330
It's okay.

276
00:13:19,660 --> 00:13:20,300
My treat.

277
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,830
I'll buy four cups and give you two cups.

278
00:13:21,830 --> 00:13:23,830
You can give the other cup to anyone.

279
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,670
Don't waste money.

280
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:29,730
Forget it. I don't want it.

281
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:34,390
Is she angry?

282
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,200
Can't you see?

283
00:13:37,740 --> 00:13:39,380
Is she angry because I want a cup of coffee?

284
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:40,010
No.

285
00:13:40,700 --> 00:13:41,340
Elly.

286
00:13:42,130 --> 00:13:43,930
You actually don't understand.

287
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:46,670
[Closed]

288
00:13:59,310 --> 00:14:00,490
I'm off work.

289
00:14:01,850 --> 00:14:02,410
Bye bye.

290
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:05,140
Bye bye.

291
00:14:15,470 --> 00:14:16,840
This can't continue.

292
00:14:17,290 --> 00:14:18,290
